<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Order Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .logo img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 160px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .order-details {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .order-item {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .seller-support {
            color: #FF9500;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .action-required {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .important {
            background-color: #fff7ed;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="Buy Box orange.png">
    </div>

    <h1>Subject: New Order Notification – Order #<%= orderId %>
    </h1>

    <p>Dear <%= sellerName %>,</p>

    <p>You have received a new order on BuyBox. Please find the order details below:</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Order Details</h2>
        <div class="order-details">
            <div class="order-item">• Order ID: <%= orderId %>
            </div>
            <div class="order-item">• Order Date: <%= orderDate %>
            </div>
            <div class="order-item">• Buyer Name: <%= customerName %>
            </div>
            <div class="order-item">• Shipping Address: <%= customerAddress %>
            </div>
            <div class="order-item">• Item(s) Ordered:</div>
            <% products.forEach(function(product) { %>
                <div class="order-item">
                    • <%= product.name %> – <%= product.quantity %> – <%= product.price %>
                </div>
                <% }); %>
                    <div class="order-item">• Order Total: <%= totalAmount %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="order-item">• Shipping Method: <%= shippingMethod %>
                    </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section action-required">
        <h2>Action Required</h2>
        <div class="order-details">
            <div class="order-item">• Please confirm and ship the order by [SHIP-BY DATE].</div>
            <div class="order-item">• Ensure that the order is shipped using the specified shipping method.</div>
            <div class="order-item">• Update the tracking details as soon as the package is dispatched.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section important">
        <h2>Important Reminders:</h2>
        <div class="order-details">
            <div class="order-item">• Late shipments may result in order cancellations or performance penalties.</div>
            <div class="order-item">• If you cannot fulfill this order, please cancel it as soon as possible.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>For more details, log in to your BuyBox Seller Central: <a href="https://emporiumsc.co.za"
            target="_blank">https://emporiumsc.co.za</a></p>

    <p>Thank you for selling on BuyBox!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>
        <span class="seller-support">BuyBox Seller Support</span>
    </p>
</body>

</html>